title: Yohannes Tilahun
text:
Yohannes Tilahun (born 16 October 1993) is an <a href="Eritrea">Eritrea</a>n <a href="Association%20football">footballer</a>. He currently plays for the <a href="Eritrea%20national%20football%20team">Eritrea national football team</a>.
International career.
Tilahun played in the <a href="2009%20CECAFA%20Cup">2009 CECAFA Cup</a> in <a href="Kenya">Kenya</a>, appearing in the 2–1 group match defeat to <a href="Rwanda%20national%20football%20team">Rwanda</a>.
